graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Port 9443/TCP]
        Controller -->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod (Multi-container)"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Router<br/>Java - Port 8033/8080]
        Adapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Go - Port 8085]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>Go - Port 8008]
        ModelServer[Model Server<br/>Triton/MLServer/OVMS]
        StorageHelper[Storage Helper<br/>Init Container]

        ModelMesh -->|routes to| Adapter
        Adapter -->|adapts protocol| ModelServer
        RESTProxy -->|converts to gRPC| ModelMesh
        StorageHelper -.->|downloads models| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR

    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| RuntimePod[Runtime Deployment]
    RuntimePod -.->|contains| ModelMesh

    Controller -->|validates via| Webhook

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        etcd[etcd<br/>StatefulSet<br/>Port 2379]
        S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>HTTPS/443]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>HTTPS/6443]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/reconciles| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|state sync| etcd
    StorageHelper -->|downloads| S3

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        KServe[KServe<br/>CRD Schema]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh/Istio<br/>Optional mTLS]
        Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>Prometheus]
    end

    Controller -->|uses CRD schema| KServe
    RuntimePod -.->|optional| ServiceMesh
    Controller -->|exposes metrics| Monitoring
    ModelMesh -->|exposes metrics| Monitoring

    Client[Client Application] -->|gRPC inference<br/>8033/TCP| ModelMesh
    Client -->|REST inference<br/>8008/TCP| RESTProxy

